{
  "stem": "12491.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe we would have married at that point, maybe he could, maybe he could have given it to us, but wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, of course, I could have gone to Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I sent out many people to Israel, but I went to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked very hard on the illegal aliyah, some of-- with the Jewish brigade-- if you're familiar with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Some with some other Zionist organizations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when the time came to go, I said, I'm going to the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- first, we organized things for the people to get things for them so they can take with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because most people were poor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not everybody was active enough, like I was, to make money, for instance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People lived day to day from the soup they were delivered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, we have helped a lot Palestine Haganah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were buying weapons and vehicles from American and English soldiers-- I mean groups.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were packing them into boxes and shipping them as agricultural equipment to Palestine, through Cyprus, Cyprus to Greece.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is what I was involved in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were collecting money from people who-- we, we being in business, knew who is big in business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we knew who to squeeze for money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We squeezed them for money, and we, we were buying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- you can't imagine what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Across the border of them-- of the English, American zone-- there was a big American PX.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know the PXs?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the captain of the PX, who was in charge of the PX-- and he had an assistant, a little Jewish fellow, Schloimela.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Schloimela was selling cigarettes by the boxes, not by 50 cartons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got through Schloimela to the captain, we started buying weapons.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
